{"tid":1362581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔 好 再 爭 論 去 唔 去 元 朗，係 一 撚 定 要 去！","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:56:59.000Z","uid":35194,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"45cf0203ba5b349298a32c3c817ee477fd7f4b01","tid":1362581,"uid":35194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"而家只要係正常既香港人都慶過火屎，你點叫人唔去？<br />\n<br />\n何妖同十八鄉班人渣係咁叫人唔好去元朗，擺明就係心入面驚到仆街，我地就更加要入元朗，如果唔係你叫香港人之後點抬起頭做人，叫屯元天大西北既巴絲如何安心？<br />\n<br />\n元朗係一撚定要去，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但要記住我地入去係<span style=\"color: red;\">反官警鄉黑</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係打黑</span>，絕對不能主動出擊</span><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日遍地開花，連政府各部門、EO都企出黎，你就知721白衣恐襲係壓倒林鄭政府既最後一根稻草。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對準政權</strong></span>，呢個垃圾政府好快就會崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n互相守護，721元朗見。"},{"pid":"b7106994d3149ed6f562cb70885e0313218751bd","tid":1362581,"uid":35194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:12:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8c960b9b39200baa6e5a64ec9c5e5f4be4ff1ca4","tid":1362581,"uid":181089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb27f7c037d8c97aa38d31d33e13dc4659ea8b0","tid":1362581,"uid":181089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037c449ca830c17fd6ad0b453c5baf3eac9a0d6e","tid":1362581,"uid":57,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"恐襲前我覺得冇必要去, 恐襲後係一定要去"},{"pid":"a9f65d4fa6a9ae683f40e7594132837efd61b57f","tid":1362581,"uid":268623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"我係元朗原居民，我絕對支持元朗「反政警黑遊行」！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361635\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cfca2559c8e50460503e1699658485147d94bd5